title: Reflexology A Practical Guide by Carol Gilbey x264 aac [MP4]
description:
Reflexology is the ancient art of accessing imbalances within the body through pressure points on the feet and hands. This involves various massage techniques to sedate or stimulate specific target areas.

This DVD takes you through many of the pressure points used during a reflexology treatment and indicates many aspects to be considered when giving or receiving this therapy.
